      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(cli): bridge inter-tool commentary events to channel progress",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nTwo related fixes to **CLI-runtime inter-tool commentary** in channel progress drafts:\n\n1. **Delivery bridge** — the missing subscriber in the shared CLI-runtime dispatch (`runCliAgentWithLifecycle`). Inter-tool commentary surfaces on the agent-event bus as `stream:\"item\", kind:\"preamble\"`, but only the assistant/reasoning/tool streams were bridged to the channel — the item/preamble stream had **no subscriber**, so commentary was dropped. This adds `createCommentaryEventBridge` → `onItemEvent` (both the primary and queued follow-up call sites).\n2. **Render in full (noCompact)** — commentary lines are assistant *prose* and must not be compacted like tool lines (file paths/args). They now carry `noCompact` so the progress-draft renderer skips per-line compaction; long commentary renders fully and spills to a new message at the channel limit rather than truncating mid-sentence.\n\nThis is **general CLI-runtime infrastructure** (claude-cli, google-gemini-cli, …), not claude-specific — it brings the CLI dispatch to parity with codex's ACP commentary. The first producer on this path is **claude-cli (#89834)**; together they close #87326 for claude-cli.\n\n## Tests\n\n- `tsgo` clean\n- `bridges CLI commentary agent events into onItemEvent for live preview` (primary + queued follow-up)\n\n## Proof (combined stack: this + #89834 producer)\n\nCaptured via a local recreation of the Mantis (telegram-desktop-proof) flow on crabbox.\n\nInter-tool commentary appears in the live progress draft (transient in non-persist mode — the recording is the evidence):\n\n![claude-cli commentary in the live progress draft](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/anagnorisis2peripeteia/openclaw/proof/commentary-persist-v2/commentary-transient.gif)\n\n**noCompact** — a long (>120-char) multi-sentence commentary line rendering in **full** (here shown in the persisted draft from the #89850 stack, same renderer):\n\n![long commentary rendered in full](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/anagnorisis2peripeteia/openclaw/proof/commentary-persist-v2/persist-accumulate.png)\n\n## Issues\n\nPart of the fix for #87326 (delivery + render half; **depends on #89834** for the claude-cli producer).\nRelated: #84486.\n",
        "branch": "fix/cli-commentary-delivery",
